{"tid":1257076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英外相就條例接受質詢 促港府就6.12衝突展開獨立調查","createTime":"2019-06-25T11:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T11:41:56.000Z","uid":262201,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e012951a2f30e8a2095ea3a8e2a60e628d4ac1d","tid":1257076,"uid":262201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:04:15.000Z","msg":"英國下議院周二舉行口頭質詢環節，工黨下議員夏爾馬（Virendra Sharma）向外相侯俊偉（Jeremy Hunt）提出質詢，要求侯俊偉透露他就香港修訂《逃犯條例》，向中方的相關部門提出了甚麼交涉，以及闡述在《中英聯合聲明》之下，英國就修例有甚麼責任。<br />\n<br />\n侯俊偉回應指，他對香港的情況仍十分關注，他曾在6月12日向香港特首表示關注，他今天又促請特區政府就6.12的暴力事件進行獨立調查，相關報告的內容將影響日後英國對香港輸出防暴裝備的許可證，在獨立報告出爐前，英國將暫停向香港輸出相關裝備。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果source：<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190625&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59755372\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190625%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59755372&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDife5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=fa452fd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190625%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59755372&h=dcea1eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190625&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59755372</a>"},{"pid":"33c5527be59f18e636d198e8a2dd995829a1ab13","tid":1257076,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"英國咀炮至叻"},{"pid":"a964b241e97a85aecd260d082783bd801634f7ce","tid":1257076,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"在獨立報告出爐前，英國將暫停向香港輸出相關裝備。<br />\n<br />\n今次算有啲動作喎"},{"pid":"97a2d96344a64ea25a1ce485d15f1f45a49bf181","tid":1257076,"uid":8600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a964b241e97a85aecd260d082783bd801634f7ce","tid":1257076,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:40:09.000Z","msg":"在獨立報告出爐前，英國將暫停向香港輸出相關裝備。<br />\n<br />\n今次算有啲動作喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T11:41:56.000Z","msg